sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Code as JIT code / executor
    participant P as JsPromise (js_promises[idx])
    participant Settle as js_promise_settle
    participant MQ as microtask ring
    participant Run as js_promise_microtask_run
    participant Next as next promise

    Code->>P: resolve(value)
    P->>Settle: js_promise_resolve_with_value
    Note over Settle: thenable? enqueue PromiseResolveThenableJob
    Settle->>P: state = FULFILLED, result = value
    loop each registered reaction i
        Settle->>MQ: js_enqueue_promise_job(bound thunk)
    end
    Note over MQ: returns to caller (async)
    MQ->>Run: js_microtask_flush pops thunk
    Run->>Run: handler_result = handler(result)
    Run->>Next: js_promise_resolve_with_value(handler_result)
    Note over Next: chains the next reaction
